d9;\"\u003e비즈니스 로직 실행\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\n\u003c!-- DB 경로 --\u003e\n\u003ch3 style=\"color:#58a6ff;font-size:1.1em;margin:24px 0 12px;\"\u003eDB 경로 (비동기)\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003ctable style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:0.9em;\"\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003cth style=\"background:#1c2333;color:#e6edf3;padding:10px 14px;text-align:left;font-weight:600;border-bottom:2px solid #30363d;\"\u003e단계\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003cth style=\"background:#1c2333;color:#e6edf3;padding:10px 14px;text-align:left;font-weight:600;border-bottom:2px solid #30363d;\"\u003e컴포넌트\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003cth style=\"background:#1c2333;color:#e6edf3;padding:10px 14px;text-align:left;font-weight:600;border-bottom:2px solid #30363d;\"\u003e설명\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e1\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#3fb950;font-weight:600;\"\u003e게임 로직\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003eDB 요청을 deque 큐에 push (채널별 mutex)\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e2\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#d29922;font-weight:600;\"\u003eDBWorker (thread_local)\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e쿼리 실행 (SP 호출 기반)\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e3\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#f78166;font-weight:600;\"\u003eCRecvQue (DBA\u0026rarr;GW)\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003eDB 결과를 GameWorker에 ACK 전달\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:none;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e4\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:none;color:#f78166;font-weight:600;\"\u003eGameWorker_DBA.cpp\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:none;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003eOnRemoteDBA 콜백에서 결과 처리 + 응답 패킷 송신\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\n\u003c!-- 응답 경로 --\u003e\n\u003ch3 style=\"color:#58a6ff;font-size:1.1em;margin:24px 0 12px;\"\u003e응답 경로 (서버 \u0026rarr; 클라이언트)\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003ctable style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:0.9em;\"\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003cth style=\"background:#1c2333;color:#e6edf3;padding:10px 14px;text-align:left;font-weight:600;border-bottom:2px solid #30363d;\"\u003e단계\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003cth style=\"background:#1c2333;color:#e6edf3;padding:10px 14px;text-align:left;font-weight:600;border-bottom:2px solid #30363d;\"\u003e컴포넌트\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003cth style=\"background:#1c2333;color:#e6edf3;padding:10px 14px;text-align:left;font-weight:600;border-bottom:2px solid #30363d;\"\u003e설명\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e1\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#f78166;font-weight:600;\"\u003eCGameWorker::Send_USER\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e게임 로직 / DBA 핸들러에서 호출 (GameWorker 단일 스레드)\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e2\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#58a6ff;font-weight:600;\"\u003eGLOBAL::SsnMngr.Find(SSNID)\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e유저의 SSNID로 CSession 포인터 조회\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e3\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#58a6ff;font-weight:600;\"\u003eCSession::SendPacket(pPacket)\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e내부 sendQueue(뮤텍스 보호)에 패킷 push; 전송 중이 아니면 즉시 async_write 개시\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:none;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e4\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:none;color:#58a6ff;font-weight:600;\"\u003eboost::asio::async_write (sendStrand)\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:none;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003eI/O 스레드(sendStrand)에서 비동기 소켓 전송; 완료 콜백에서 다음 패킷 연속 처리\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"padding:14px 20px;border-radius:8px;margin:12px 0;font-size:0.9em;color:#c9d1d9;border-left:3px solid #d29922;background:rgba(210,153,34,0.08);\"\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"color:#c9d1d9;margin:0;\"\u003e\u003cstrong style=\"color:#d29922;\"\u003e핵심 특성:\u003c/strong\u003e 응답 패킷은 GameWorker 스레드에서 \u003cstrong style=\"color:#e6edf3;\"\u003eCSession::SendPacket을 직접 호출\u003c/strong\u003e한다. 별도의 FastSendQue / StableSendQue 경유 없이 세션 내부 sendQueue에 적재되고, 실제 소켓 I/O는 Boost.Asio sendStrand(I/O 스레드)에서 비동기로 처리된다. \u003ccode style=\"background:#1c2333;color:#f78166;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:4px;font-size:0.88em;font-family:Consolas,monospace;\"\u003eCNetWorker::Send\u003c/code\u003e(StableSendQue) 및 \u003ccode style=\"background:#1c2333;color:#f78166;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:4px;font-size:0.88em;font-family:Consolas,monospace;\"\u003eFastSend\u003c/code\u003e는 현재 게임 로직에서 주석 처리되어 미사용이다.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c!-- 5. 비동기 처리와 정합성 보호 --\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"async\" style=\"background:#161b22;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:12px;padding:28px 32px;margin-bottom:24px;\"\u003e\n\u003ch2 style=\"color:#e6edf3;font-size:1.4em;margin:0 0 20px;padding-bottom:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;\"\u003e5. 비동기 처리와 정합성 보호\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv style=\"padding:14px 20px;border-radius:8px;margin:0 0 16px;font-size:0.9em;color:#c9d1d9;border-left:3px solid #58a6ff;background:rgba(88,166,255,0.08);\"\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"color:#c9d1d9;margin:0;\"\u003ewot_server는 \u003cstrong style=\"color:#f78166;\"\u003eGameWorker 단일 스레드\u003c/strong\u003e 구조를 사용하기 때문에 게임 메모리 상태의 동시 접근 문제는 비교적 안전하게 제어된다. 하지만 DB, ASE, BUS, Redis 같은 외부 작업은 \u003cstrong style=\"color:#e6edf3;\"\u003e별도 스레드 또는 외부 시스템을 통해 비동기로 처리\u003c/strong\u003e된다.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp style=\"color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e기존 분석에서도 GameWorker, DB 채널 스레드, ASE Worker, BUS 스레드, Redis Worker가 분리되어 있으며, 결과는 다시 GameWorker에서 처리되는 구조로 정리되어 있다.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp style=\"color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e따라서 서버 로직은 다음과 같은 전제를 가져야 한다.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv style=\"padding:14px 20px;border-radius:8px;margin:12px 0;font-size:0.9em;color:#c9d1d9;border-left:3px solid #d29922;background:rgba(210,153,34,0.08);\"\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"color:#c9d1d9;margin:0 0 8px;\"\u003e\u003cstrong style=\"color:#d29922;\"\u003e핵심 전제 1:\u003c/strong\u003e GameWorker는 단일 스레드지만, 서버 전체 처리는 \u003cstrong style=\"color:#e6edf3;\"\u003e완전한 동기 흐름이 아니다.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"color:#c9d1d9;margin:0;\"\u003e\u003cstrong style=\"color:#d29922;\"\u003e핵심 전제 2:\u003c/strong\u003e DB에 갔다 오는 동안 \u003cstrong style=\"color:#e6edf3;\"\u003e같은 유저의 후속 패킷이 처리될 수 있으므로\u003c/strong\u003e, 중간 상태를 보호하기 위해 TimeLock과 선처리/후처리가 필요하다.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp style=\"color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e결국 \u003cstrong style=\"color:#e6edf3;\"\u003eTimeLock / 선처리 / 후처리\u003c/strong\u003e는 단일 스레드 게임 로직과 비동기 DB 처리 사이에서 발생하는 정합성 문제를 막기 위한 방어 구조라고 볼 수 있다.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c!-- 처리 흐름 다이어그램 --\u003e\n\u003ch3 style=\"color:#58a6ff;font-size:1.1em;margin:24px 0 12px;\"\u003eTimeLock / 선처리 / 후처리 흐름\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"background:#1c2333;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:8px;padding:24px 20px;margin:12px 0;\"\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv style=\"display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:16px;\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"display:inline-block;background:#0d1117;border:2px solid #f78166;border-radius:8px;padding:8px 14px;text-align:center;\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"color:#f78166;font-weight:700;font-size:0.88em;\"\u003eGameWorker\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:0.75em;\"\u003e단일 스레드\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:1.1em;line-height:2.5;\"\u003e\u0026harr;\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"display:inline-block;background:#0d1117;border:2px solid #d29922;border-radius:8px;padding:8px 14px;text-align:center;\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"color:#d29922;font-weight:700;font-size:0.88em;\"\u003eDB Worker\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:0.75em;\"\u003e비동기 처리\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv style=\"text-align:center;\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"display:inline-block;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #3fb950;border-radius:8px;padding:10px 20px;color:#3fb950;font-weight:600;font-size:0.9em;\"\u003e1. 선처리 (유효성 검사, 자원 선점)\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"text-align:center;color:#8b949e;font-size:1.1em;margin:6px 0;\"\u003e\u0026#9660;\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"text-align:center;\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"display:inline-block;background:#0d1117;border:2px solid #f78166;border-radius:8px;padding:10px 20px;text-align:center;\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"color:#f78166;font-weight:700;font-size:0.9em;\"\u003e2. TimeLock 설정 — CUserContentBlockMask\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:0.8em;margin-top:4px;\"\u003e처리 중인 콘텐츠를 Block하여 재진입 방지\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"text-align:center;color:#8b949e;font-size:1.1em;margin:6px 0;\"\u003e\u0026#9660;\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"text-align:center;\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"display:inline-block;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #d29922;border-radius:8px;padding:10px 20px;color:#d29922;font-weight:600;font-size:0.9em;\"\u003e3. DB 요청 전송 (비동기)\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"text-align:center;color:#8b949e;font-size:0.82em;margin:4px 0;\"\u003eDB 응답 대기 중 — 같은 유저의 후속 패킷 도착 가능\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"text-align:center;\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"display:inline-block;background:#0d1117;border:1px dashed #d29922;border-radius:8px;padding:8px 20px;color:#8b949e;font-size:0.82em;\"\u003e4. 후속 패킷 도착 → TimeLock(BlockMask)으로 재진입 차단\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"text-align:center;color:#8b949e;font-size:1.1em;margin:6px 0;\"\u003e\u0026#9660;\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"text-align:center;\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"display:inline-block;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #bc8cff;border-radius:8px;padding:10px 20px;color:#bc8cff;font-weight:600;font-size:0.9em;\"\u003e5. DB ACK 도착 (OnRemoteDBA 콜백)\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"text-align:center;color:#8b949e;font-size:1.1em;margin:6px 0;\"\u003e\u0026#9660;\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"text-align:center;\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"display:inline-block;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #3fb950;border-radius:8px;padding:10px 20px;color:#3fb950;font-weight:600;font-size:0.9em;\"\u003e6. 후처리 (결과 적용, TimeLock 해제)\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c!-- TimeLock 설명 --\u003e\n\u003ch3 style=\"color:#58a6ff;font-size:1.1em;margin:24px 0 12px;\"\u003eTimeLock — CUserContentBlockMask\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"padding:14px 20px;border-radius:8px;margin:12px 0;font-size:0.9em;color:#c9d1d9;border-left:3px solid #f78166;background:rgba(247,129,102,0.08);\"\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"color:#c9d1d9;margin:0;\"\u003e\u003cstrong style=\"color:#f78166;\"\u003eTimeLock\u003c/strong\u003e이란 DB 응답이 오기 전까지 \u003cstrong style=\"color:#e6edf3;\"\u003e같은 작업이 다시 실행되지 않도록 막는 임시 잠금 장치\u003c/strong\u003e이다. wot_server에서는 \u003ccode style=\"background:#1c2333;color:#f78166;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:4px;font-size:0.88em;font-family:Consolas,monospace;\"\u003eCUserContentBlockMask\u003c/code\u003e로 처리 중인 콘텐츠를 막아 재진입을 방지한다.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c!-- 6. DB 계층 --\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"db\" style=\"background:#161b22;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:12px;padding:28px 32px;margin-bottom:24px;\"\u003e\n\u003ch2 style=\"color:#e6edf3;font-size:1.4em;margin:0 0 20px;padding-bottom:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;\"\u003e6. DB 계층 구조\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 style=\"color:#58a6ff;font-size:1.1em;margin:8px 0 12px;\"\u003e12종 DB 인스턴스\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003ctable style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:0.9em;\"\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003cth style=\"background:#1c2333;color:#e6edf3;padding:10px 14px;text-align:left;font-weight:600;border-bottom:2px solid #30363d;\"\u003e타입\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003cth style=\"background:#1c2333;color:#e6edf3;padding:10px 14px;text-align:left;font-weight:600;border-bottom:2px solid #30363d;\"\u003e클래스\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003cth style=\"background:#1c2333;color:#e6edf3;padding:10px 14px;text-align:left;font-weight:600;border-bottom:2px solid #30363d;\"\u003e채널\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003cth style=\"background:#1c2333;color:#e6edf3;padding:10px 14px;text-align:left;font-weight:600;border-bottom:2px solid #30363d;\"\u003e용도\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#d29922;font-weight:600;\"\u003eACCOUNT_DB\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003eCAccountDB\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003eUSER\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14p