ottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e글로벌 랭킹\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#d29922;font-weight:600;\"\u003eRANKING_DB\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003eCRankingDB\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003eUSER\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e서버 랭킹\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#d29922;font-weight:600;\"\u003eBATTLE_ROYAL_DB\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003eCBattleRoyalDB\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003eUSER\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e배틀로얄\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:none;color:#d29922;font-weight:600;\"\u003eWEB_DB\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:none;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003eCWebDB\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:none;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003eUSER\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:none;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e웹 연동\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 style=\"color:#58a6ff;font-size:1.1em;margin:24px 0 12px;\"\u003eTLDB 라이브러리 구조\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003ctable style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:0.9em;\"\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003cth style=\"background:#1c2333;color:#e6edf3;padding:10px 14px;text-align:left;font-weight:600;border-bottom:2px solid #30363d;\"\u003e클래스\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003cth style=\"background:#1c2333;color:#e6edf3;padding:10px 14px;text-align:left;font-weight:600;border-bottom:2px solid #30363d;\"\u003e역할\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#f78166;font-weight:600;\"\u003eConnection\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003eODBC SQLHDBC 래핑, 재연결 감지\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#f78166;font-weight:600;\"\u003eDBPool\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e커넥션 풀 (queue FIFO, size=2)\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:none;color:#f78166;font-weight:600;\"\u003eCQuery / GenerateQuery\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:none;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003eSP 호출 기반 쿼리 (BIND/DEFINE 매크로)\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv style=\"padding:14px 20px;border-radius:8px;margin:12px 0;font-size:0.9em;color:#c9d1d9;border-left:3px solid #58a6ff;background:rgba(88,166,255,0.08);\"\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"color:#c9d1d9;margin:0;\"\u003e\u003cstrong style=\"color:#58a6ff;\"\u003eRedis:\u003c/strong\u003e 범용 캐시가 아닌 \u003cstrong style=\"color:#e6edf3;\"\u003e랭킹 전용\u003c/strong\u003e (Sorted Set + Hash, Write-Through 패턴). ASE Worker 기반 비동기 처리.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c!-- 7. Bus 통신 --\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"bus\" style=\"background:#161b22;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:12px;padding:28px 32px;margin-bottom:24px;\"\u003e\n\u003ch2 style=\"color:#e6edf3;font-size:1.4em;margin:0 0 20px;padding-bottom:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;\"\u003e7. 서버간 통신 (Bus 시스템) — InternalBusManager 담당\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv style=\"padding:14px 20px;border-radius:8px;margin:0 0 16px;font-size:0.9em;color:#c9d1d9;border-left:3px solid #bc8cff;background:rgba(188,140,255,0.08);\"\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"color:#c9d1d9;margin:0;\"\u003e\u003cstrong style=\"color:#bc8cff;\"\u003eInternalBusManager\u003c/strong\u003e가 실제 서버간 통신을 전담합니다. \u003cstrong style=\"color:#d29922;\"\u003eNxNet\u003c/strong\u003e은 기능상 서버간 TCP 연결을 지원하나 현실에서는 \u003cstrong style=\"color:#d29922;\"\u003e모니터링 툴에서만\u003c/strong\u003e 사용됩니다. 게임 로직의 모든 서버간 메시지는 InternalBusManager → RabbitMQ 경로를 사용합니다.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c!-- MQ 설명 --\u003e\n\u003ch3 style=\"color:#58a6ff;font-size:1.1em;margin:8px 0 12px;\"\u003eMQ(RabbitMQ) 동작 방식\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"text-align:center;margin:12px 0;\"\u003e\n\u003cimg src=\"figure5.webp\" alt=\"RabbitMQ MQ 구조\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #30363d;\"\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"padding:14px 20px;border-radius:8px;margin:12px 0;font-size:0.9em;color:#c9d1d9;border-left:3px solid #bc8cff;background:rgba(188,140,255,0.08);\"\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"color:#c9d1d9;margin:0;\"\u003eMQ는 메시지를 큐에 넣고 Consumer에게 전달해주는 역할까지는 해주지만, 그 메시지를 실제로 어떻게 처리할지는 Consumer 책임이다. 특히 \u003cstrong style=\"color:#e6edf3;\"\u003eack 타이밍, 실패 시 재시도, 중복 메시지 처리, DB 트랜잭션과의 정합성\u003c/strong\u003e은 RabbitMQ가 자동으로 해결해주지 않는다. 그래서 받는 쪽에서 중복 처리 방지, 처리 이력, 에러 처리, 재시도 정책을 제대로 설계해야 안정적으로 사용할 수 있다.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"padding:14px 20px;border-radius:8px;margin:12px 0;font-size:0.9em;color:#c9d1d9;border-left:3px solid #d29922;background:rgba(210,153,34,0.08);\"\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"color:#c9d1d9;margin:0;\"\u003e\u003cstrong style=\"color:#d29922;\"\u003e주의 — ACK 비보장 / TCP-IP와의 차이:\u003c/strong\u003e MQ는 \u003cstrong style=\"color:#e6edf3;\"\u003eACK가 보장되지 않는 방식\u003c/strong\u003e이다. TCP-IP처럼 패킷 전달 자체를 양 끝단이 확인하고 재전송을 보장하는 연결 지향 통신과는 근본적으로 다르다. MQ는 큐에 넣은 뒤 Consumer가 꺼내갔는지 여부만 관리할 뿐이며, Consumer가 메시지를 꺼내간 후 처리 도중 실패하더라도 RabbitMQ 자체는 이를 인지하지 못한다.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv style=\"background:#1c2333;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:8px;padding:24px 20px;margin:12px 0;\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:20px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"display:inline-block;background:#0d1117;border:2px solid #3fb950;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 20px;text-align:center;\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"color:#3fb950;font-weight:600;font-size:0.95em;\"\u003eGameServer 1\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"color:#bc8cff;font-size:0.82em;font-weight:600;margin-top:4px;\"\u003e★ InternalBusManager\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:0.78em;\"\u003e서버간 통신 담당\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:0.78em;\"\u003ePublish/Broad\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"text-align:center;color:#8b949e;font-size:1.2em;\"\u003e\u0026rarr;\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"display:inline-block;background:#0d1117;border:2px solid #bc8cff;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 20px;text-align:center;\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"color:#bc8cff;font-weight:600;font-size:0.95em;\"\u003eRabbitMQ\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:0.78em;\"\u003eAMQP-CPP\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:0.78em;\"\u003eExchange / Queue\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"text-align:center;color:#8b949e;font-size:1.2em;\"\u003e\u0026rarr;\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"display:inline-block;background:#0d1117;border:2px solid #3fb950;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 20px;text-align:center;\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"color:#3fb950;font-weight:600;font-size:0.95em;\"\u003eGameServer 2\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"color:#bc8cff;font-size:0.82em;font-weight:600;margin-top:4px;\"\u003e★ InternalBusManager\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:0.78em;\"\u003eBusDispatcher\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:0.78em;\"\u003eopcode \u0026rarr; Handler\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv style=\"margin-top:16px;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:8px;border:1px dashed #d29922;background:rgba(210,153,34,0.05);text-align:center;\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"color:#d29922;font-size:0.82em;font-weight:600;\"\u003e※ NxNet (Windows IOCP): 기능상 서버간 통신 지원 — 실사용: 모니터링 툴 전용, 게임 로직에서 미사용\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 style=\"color:#58a6ff;font-size:1.1em;margin:24px 0 12px;\"\u003e주요 BusHandler 목록\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003ctable style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:0.9em;\"\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003cth style=\"background:#1c2333;color:#e6edf3;padding:10px 14px;text-align:left;font-weight:600;border-bottom:2px solid #30363d;\"\u003eHandler\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003cth style=\"background:#1c2333;color:#e6edf3;padding:10px 14px;text-align:left;font-weight:600;border-bottom:2px solid #30363d;\"\u003e컨텐츠\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#3fb950;font-weight:600;\"\u003eAllianceWarsBusHandler\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e연맹전\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#3fb950;font-weight:600;\"\u003eServerWarsBusHandler\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e서버대전\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#3fb950;font-weight:600;\"\u003eArenaBusHandler\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e아레나\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#3fb950;font-weight:600;\"\u003eServerInvasionBusHandler\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e서버 침공\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#3fb950;font-weight:600;\"\u003eEpicBattleFrontLineBusHandler\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e에픽배틀 전선\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#3fb950;font-weight:600;\"\u003eTrenchWarfareBusHandler\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e참호전\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#3fb950;font-weight:600;\"\u003eBattleModeBusManager\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e배틀모드\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:none;color:#3fb950;font-weight:600;\"\u003eCombineEventBusHandler\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd style=\"padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:none;color:#c9d1d9;\"\u003e몬스터 처치 이벤트\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c!-- 8. Manager 분류 --\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"managers\" style=\"background:#161b22;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:12px;padding:28px 32px;margin-bottom:24px;\"\u003e\n\u003ch2 style=\"color:#e6edf3;font-size:1.4em;margin:0 0 20px;padding-bottom:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;\"\u003e8. 게임 로직 Manager 카테고리 분류\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv style=\"padding:14px 20px;border-radius:8px;margin:0 0 16px;font-size:0.9em;color:#c9d1d9;border-left:3px solid #58a6ff;background:rgba(88,166,255,0.08);\"\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"color:#c9d1d9;margin:0;\"\u003eOBJECTS/ 디렉토리에 \u003cstrong style=\"color:#e6edf3;\"\u003e130개 이상의 Manager 클래스\u003c/strong\u003e가 존재합니다. 대부분 \u003ccode style=\"background:#1c2333;color:#f78166;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:4px;font-size:0.88em;font-family:Consolas,monospace;\"\u003enx::Singleton\u0026lt;T\u0026gt;\u003c/code\u003e 패턴으로 구현되며, CGameServer의 BIND_SCHEDULE로 Update가 등록됩니다.\u003c/p\u003e\n\