<script>
/* 웹 편집기 (셸 내장) — DATA 직접 편집 + 즉시 미리보기 + 파일 열기/저장(File System Access) */
(function(){
  let feTab='projects', _fileHandle=null, _t=null;
  const TABS=[['profile','프로필'],['projects','프로젝트'],['hist','연혁'],['career','경력'],['cover','자기소개서'],['skills','보유 기술'],['edu','학력·병역'],['portfolio','포트폴리오'],['menu','메뉴']];
  const SEC_TYPES=['profile','skills','coverletter','career','projects','history','portfolio','education'];
  const E=id=>document.getElementById(id);
  const ed=E('edDrawer'), body=E('edBody');
  const fi=(sec,f,v,ph)=>`<input type="text" data-sec="${sec}" data-field="${f}" value="${_esc(v||'')}" placeholder="${ph||''}">`;
  const empty=n=>`<div style="color:var(--muted);padding:24px;text-align:center">${n} 항목이 없습니다. 아래 “+ 추가”.</div>`;
  function toast(m){ let t=E('_feToast'); if(!t){t=document.createElement('div');t.id='_feToast';t.style.cssText='position:fixed;bottom:80px;right:24px;background:#222;color:#fff;padding:8px 16px;border-radius:8px;font-size:13px;z-index:1001;opacity:0;transition:.2s';document.body.appendChild(t);} t.textContent=m;t.style.opacity='1';clearTimeout(t._h);t._h=setTimeout(()=>{t.style.opacity='0';},1600); }
  function feNav(){ const want={profile:'profile',projects:'projects',hist:'history',career:'career',cover:'coverletter',skills:'skills',edu:'profile',portfolio:'portfolio'}[feTab];
    const tree=buildMenuTree(); let found=null;
    for(const g of tree){ for(const it of g.items){ if(it.type===want){ found=it.section; break; } } if(found)break; }
    if(found) currentSection=found;
    if(feTab==='edu') currentView='timeline';        // 학력·병역 탭 → 타임라인(학력) 미리보기
    else if(currentView==='timeline') currentView='summary';
    render(); }
  function reb(){ clearTimeout(_t); _t=setTimeout(render,180); }
  function pProfile(){ const p=DATA.profile||(DATA.profile={}); const r=(f,ph)=>`<label class="fe-fl"><span>${ph}</span>${fi('profile',f,p[f],ph)}</label>`;
    return `<div class="fe-proj"><div class="fe-drop" data-drop="profimg">${p.photo?`<img class="fe-thumb" style="max-height:90px;width:90px;height:90px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:50%" src="${_esc(p.photo)}" alt="">`:''}<div>프로필 사진을 <b>드래그</b>하거나 <label class="fe-pick">파일 선택<input type="file" accept="image/*" data-profimg="1" style="display:none"></label>${p.photo?` · <a href="javascript:void 0" data-act="clearprofimg" style="color:var(--muted)">제거</a>`:''}</div></div>${r('name','이름')}${r('title','직함')}<label class="fe-fl"><span>소개</span><textarea data-sec="profile" data-field="objective" placeholder="한두 문장 소개">${_esc(p.objective||'')}</textarea></label><label class="fe-fl"><span>브라우저 탭 제목 (선택)</span><input type="text" data-sec="doctitle" data-field="doc_title" value="${_esc(DATA.doc_title||'')}" placeholder="비우면 '{이름} 이력서'"></label><div class="fe-grid">${fi('profile','phone',p.phone,'연락처')}${fi('profile','email',p.email,'이메일')}${fi('profile','location',p.location,'거주지')}${fi('profile','birth',p.birth,'생년월일')}${fi('profile','total_career',p.total_career,'총 경력')}${fi('profile','available',p.available,'가용 시점')}</div></div>`; }
  function pProj(){ const P=DATA.projects||(DATA.projects=[]);
    return P.map((p,pi)=>{ const secs=(p.sections||[]).map((s,si)=>`<div class="fe-sec${s.highlight?' hi':''}"><div class="fe-srow"><input type="text" data-sec="proj" data-pi="${pi}" data-si="${si}" data-field="group" value="${_esc(s.group||'')}" placeholder="그룹(서브프로젝트, 선택)"></div><div class="fe-srow"><input type="text" data-sec="proj" data-pi="${pi}" data-si="${si}" data-field="title" value="${_esc(s.title||'')}" placeholder="소제목 (예: 성과)"><label class="fe-lbl"><input type="checkbox" data-sec="proj" data-pi="${pi}" data-si="${si}" data-field="highlight" ${s.highlight?'checked':''}> 성과강조</label><button class="fe-del" data-act="delsec" data-pi="${pi}" data-si="${si}">섹션삭제</button></div><textarea data-sec="proj" data-pi="${pi}" data-si="${si}" data-field="body" placeholder="본문(마크다운)">${_esc(s.body||'')}</textarea></div>`).join('');
      return `<div class="fe-proj"><div class="fe-h"><b>#${pi+1}</b><input type="text" data-sec="proj" data-pi="${pi}" data-field="name" value="${_esc(p.name||'')}" placeholder="프로젝트 제목"><button class="fe-del" data-act="delproj" data-pi="${pi}">✕</button></div><div class="fe-grid"><input type="text" data-sec="proj" data-pi="${pi}" data-field="game" value="${_esc((p.game||[]).join(', '))}" placeholder="게임코드(쉼표)"><input type="text" data-sec="proj" data-pi="${pi}" data-field="role" value="${_esc(p.role||'')}" placeholder="역할"><input type="text" data-sec="proj" data-pi="${pi}" data-field="period" value="${_esc(p.period||'')}" placeholder="기간"><input type="text" data-sec="proj" data-pi="${pi}" data-field="appeal" value="${_esc(p.appeal||'')}" placeholder="어필 포인트"></div>${secs}<button class="fe-addsec" data-act="addsec" data-pi="${pi}">+ 섹션</button></div>`;
    }).join('')||empty('프로젝트'); }
  function pHist(){ const H=DATA.history||(DATA.history=[]);
    return `<div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin:0 0 8px">위키 상세와 별개의 간단 연대표입니다. 메뉴 탭에서 종류를 <b>history</b>로 한 메뉴를 추가하면 사이드바에 “연혁”으로 표시됩니다. ↑↓로 순서 변경.</div>`
      + H.map((h,hi)=>`<div class="fe-proj"><div class="fe-h"><b>#${hi+1}</b><input type="text" data-sec="hist" data-hi="${hi}" data-field="name" value="${_esc(h.name||'')}" placeholder="프로젝트 / 이력 이름"><button class="fe-ord" data-act="histup" data-hi="${hi}" ${hi===0?'disabled':''} title="위로">↑</button><button class="fe-ord" data-act="histdown" data-hi="${hi}" ${hi===H.length-1?'disabled':''} title="아래로">↓</button><button class="fe-del" data-act="delhist" data-hi="${hi}">✕</button></div>
        <div class="fe-grid"><input type="text" data-sec="hist" data-hi="${hi}" data-field="period" value="${_esc(h.period||'')}" placeholder="기간 (예: 2018~2020)"><input type="text" data-sec="hist" data-hi="${hi}" data-field="role" value="${_esc(h.role||'')}" placeholder="역할 (선택)"></div>
        <label class="fe-fl"><span>한 줄 설명 (선택)</span><textarea data-sec="hist" data-hi="${hi}" data-field="desc">${_esc(h.desc||'')}</textarea></label></div>`).join('')||empty('연혁'); }
  function pCareer(){ const C=DATA.career||(DATA.career=[]);
    return C.map((c,ci)=>`<div class="fe-proj"><div class="fe-h"><b>#${ci+1}</b><input type="text" data-sec="career" data-ci="${ci}" data-field="company" value="${_esc(c.company||'')}" placeholder="타이틀(회사/프로젝트)"><button class="fe-del" data-act="delcareer" data-ci="${ci}">✕</button></div><div class="fe-grid"><input type="text" data-sec="career" data-ci="${ci}" data-field="role" value="${_esc(c.role||'')}" placeholder="담당 직무"><input type="text" data-sec="career" data-ci="${ci}" data-field="period" value="${_esc(c.period||'')}" placeholder="기간"><input type="text" data-sec="career" data-ci="${ci}" data-field="department" value="${_esc(c.department||'')}" placeholder="서브타이틀"><input type="text" data-sec="career" data-ci="${ci}" data-field="domain" value="${_esc((c.domain||[]).join(', '))}" placeholder="도메인(쉼표)"></div><label class="fe-fl"><span>요약</span><textarea data-sec="career" data-ci="${ci}" data-field="summary">${_esc(c.summary||'')}</textarea></label><label class="fe-fl"><span>상세(한 줄=한 항목)</span><textarea data-sec="career" data-ci="${ci}" data-field="bullets">${_esc((c.bullets||[]).join('\n'))}</textarea></label></div>`).join('')||empty('경력'); }
  function pCover(){ const cl=DATA.coverletter||(DATA.coverletter={sections:[]}); const S=cl.sections||(cl.sections=[]);
    return S.map((s,ci)=>`<div class="fe-proj"><div class="fe-h"><input type="text" data-sec="cover" data-ci="${ci}" data-field="title" value="${_esc(s.title||'')}" placeholder="소제목"><button class="fe-del" data-act="delcover" data-ci="${ci}">✕</button></div><textarea data-sec="cover" data-ci="${ci}" data-field="content" placeholder="본문(마크다운)">${_esc(s.content||'')}</textarea></div>`).join('')||empty('자기소개서'); }
  function pSkills(){ const sk=(window._skillGroups?_skillGroups():(DATA.skills||(DATA.skills={})));
    return Object.keys(sk).map(k=>{ const c=sk[k]||{};
      const items=(c.items||[]).map((it,ii)=>`<div class="fe-sec"><div class="fe-srow"><input type="text" data-sec="skillitem" data-key="${_esc(k)}" data-ii="${ii}" data-field="name" value="${_esc(it.name||'')}" placeholder="기술명 (예: C/C++)"><button class="fe-del" data-act="delskillitem" data-key="${_esc(k)}" data-ii="${ii}">삭제</button></div>
